Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun, your report please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:36.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:41.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Storage reports that we're almost out of gunpowder.{武器庫の報告によると、弾薬の備蓄がそろそろ尽きるそうです}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to replenish our supplies before the next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got new recruits too, so we probably need new weapons too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:48.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:50.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make today's mission a descent to Guild.{(若様?)、本日の作戦はギルド降下作戦と行きましょう}{FOTC: 分かったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,D{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Descent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of not good with heights...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:10.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not descending from the sky, we're going down underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh what, just underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, underground?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:17.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place deep underground that we call Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:19.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our comrades are making weapons there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:22.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's there so that Angel doesn't find out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:28.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If she took down Guild, we'd lose our source of ammunition and any chances of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:32.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be headed your way tonight.{FOTC: Want "tonight" in there?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave deactivating the traps to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, tonight then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going with everyone present here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to leave Noda behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot's probably just doing whatever he wants again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And heave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on don't stand around, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've been to Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an idiot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi, I don't recognize you as one of us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why on earth did he go out of his way to wait here for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun likes to stress the importance of the moment.{moment, circumstances, situation?}{FOTC: scenario, situation, screenplay}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:48.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't particularly want to be accepted by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it'll be 1000— {BLARHGG!}{貴様、今度は千回死なせ・・・}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:03.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Defensive positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The traps haven't been deactivated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:13.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The route to Guild has several anti{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Angel instant{\fnNyala}-{\fn}fatality traps set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that they're all still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:17.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they forgot to deactivate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they trying to wipe us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Guild used their own judgment and reset the traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There could only be one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wild then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys at Guild would do this even though they know we're on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you don't understand yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, it's not like we'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, we will experience the pain of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the part I don't like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:54.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Guild's whereabouts are discovered and they fall, we'll no longer be able to replenish ammo or replace broken weapons.{銃弾の補充も壊れた武器の補綴も利かなくなる}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How would we be able to fight Angel in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guild's decision was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go after Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,While the traps are still set?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel will be taken down by the traps right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The traps will only slow her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what kind of traps are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are all sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, one's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuckin' crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He got caught, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else seems to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it okay not to rescue him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave him alone he'll find his way above ground on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:27.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I quite like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:34.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.{マジ無理だぜ ? check}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trap that shuts you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget something so important!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How thoughtless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something dangerous is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.22,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if you touch that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:05.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll cut your body clean in half.{最高の切れ味で胴体を真っ二つにしてくれるぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The second beam is coming!{第二射来るぞ！ check}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get under it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The third beam is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the third beam again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,X'er!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to avoid that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, just do what you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It opened, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim this time was Matsushita{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no helping it with his build.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy needs to go on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That must have been a pretty terrible sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right in front of him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you made it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, even if you get cut into pieces, you'll return to normal after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The trap's been activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:09.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling comes down in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.00,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I said don't forget things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,TK!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Run to her and hug her tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:18.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. {???な}{FOTC: 助かったな}{FOTC: Thanks.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,TK's sacrifice will be—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sacrificed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let his sacrifice go to waste, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too heavy, I can't hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should Otonashi and I drop down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, don't decide things on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be good to lose our forces all at once here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, hurry and climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it, Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have a choice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a sadist, aren't you.{FOTC: Yes. With my legs around your waist and my soles on your ○○○○○.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:20.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulders next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Stop resting and hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I grab?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere! Do what you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll fall like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she smell so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you facing this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Will you hurry up and climb?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold yourself up using that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:15.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Hinata—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.71,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,He became a precious sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're down to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:24.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well to survive, newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one will be you.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< 10:33 >
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A water trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So he can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit is this way. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is something like that—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That puppy's going to be washed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a blunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:36.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a toy!{Norg: I was tricked, it's a toy!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Shiina{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san fell prey to a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That an anti{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Angel trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, you can tell just by looking at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:46.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her weakness is her love for cute things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually pretty cute of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she'll be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:10.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If this were a real army, everyone would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a horrible leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're anti{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Angel traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd be useless if they weren't this effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to dry off these clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:35.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how you can command those crazy guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you get chosen as the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was the first to rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Against Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I kept my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:53.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were alive, before you came to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Including me, four siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:02.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the eldest, with two younger sisters and a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:08.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents did well in their jobs, so we were a really wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our house was surrounded by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost like a holiday home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our parents were out that afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Some men we didn't know came into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They were wearing balaclavas even though it was the middle of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:28.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could immediately tell that they were up to no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:32.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that as the eldest, I had to protect my siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was no way I could, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They were after money, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But they couldn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:48.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran around smashing windows and TVs, and started to get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:54.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they thought up the worst possible thing for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl, you're the eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:01.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have told you where the valuables are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:09.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "If there's an earthquake, take it and run," or, "If a burglar comes, give it to them and tell them to go away."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have told you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't tell me anything like that!{FOTC: Obviously, her family preferred 'family' over things of, ahem, real value.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, why don't you go search for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:25.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't like it, you might have to say goodbye to one of these kids here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One every ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back with one in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:34.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I desperately searched the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My head was in so much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was nauseous and about to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But their lives were on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:47.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't know of anything valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry! I need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I bring this big vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's this heavy, it has to be really valuable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The police came thirty minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:23.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care if I become a water flea or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:34.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All I want to do is fight God if he really does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We hadn't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:45.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet on that day, even with my confidence as an older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,everything I wanted to protect was stolen from me within the space of 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could it be that unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:54.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept that kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong aren't you, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:03.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had memories like that, I think I'd want to vanish as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:12.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't commit suicide or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone who committed suicide bother fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, there's no one in this world who died by suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She got here safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys make weapons here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to fight your way through all those traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, where's Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She stopped for a while, but she's on the move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She set another one off!{また掛かった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:29.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's close...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're abandoning this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we can't just stop making weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important isn't locations or weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:42.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, nothing that has life can be created.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, things that just have form can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:59.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the method and means to make something, there's no problem creating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even create it out of dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:07.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, efficiency became prioritized and now all we do is make replicas in this factory.{だが、いつからか効率優先となり、こんな工場でレプリカばかりを作る仕事に慣れきってしまった}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaa{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san...{FOTC: Wow Wiki.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this guy in high school too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:16.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, we just breathe life into something that looks like what we remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head for Old Guild then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place we abandoned long ago.{長く捨て置いた場所だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:25.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left there, but there are mountains of dirt.{FOTC: There isn't anything left there, but there are mountains of dirt.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get up to ground level from there too.{あそこからなら地上へ戻れる}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll blow it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't hand over Old Guild to Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:35.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sole remaining place for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:45.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your only necessary belongings are your memories and your pride as a craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!{Norg: answer to the above question... rather than a translation here lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, prepare the explosives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:55.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no more traps left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To buy some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing for me to do down there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:39.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's responding too quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She can hold her own in close combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Load the barrel!{弾込め！ check}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really do that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:04.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:04.18,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and raise it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Delay {google'd it and reply 647 in this thread mentioned it http://hideyoshi.2ch.net/test/read.cgi/anime/1270811700/}{FOTC: I hear it as that too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you guys can pull through if you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't look like it was easy to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!{行くぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:53.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:56.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The cannon... {check}{Norg: I guess もう大隊が・・・ }{FOTC: 砲台体が...}{FOTC: The cannon...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't just put together stuff we don't know remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.86,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just put random things together!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel's getting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Use these on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The evacuation's complete! {check}{全員退避完了！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're blowing up Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:16.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:18.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many years its been...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There seriously is nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:48.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get as much dirt as you want if you poke around the walls.{壁をつついたらどれだけでも土くれ落ちてくるわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one run down joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:55.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you idiots awake yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:03.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We blew up Guild, and Angel with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:04.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Relay this to everyone.{check}{総員??る current TL a guess}{FOTC: 総員に告ぐ}{FOTC: Relay to everyone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Head to Old Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:09.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll replenish supplies as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:13.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Head to Old Guild before Angel recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:15.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, hurry up you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:19.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved her without thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:20.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:24.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All I want to do is fight God if he really does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:28.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:30.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:34.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder everyone follows you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:40.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fine leader.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< Preview >
Comment: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:16.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the new song...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:18.68,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...a ballad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.85,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what you can call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You couldn't sing the song you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:21.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:22.31,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Really bad fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.35,0:24:22.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Also, pump it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:22.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.31,0:24:23.10,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's happening exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.64,0:24:23.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One second you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:23.94,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel's appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:24.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:24.73,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:25.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you in a different light.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:25.90,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:29.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,don't touch it!
